      • lerp

        public AircraftState lerp(AircraftState other,
                          double t)
        Linearly interpolate between this state and another state. when t = 0.0 it is entirely this state when t = 1.0 it is entirely the other state
        Parameters:
        other - other state to interpolate with
        t - factor between 0.0 and 1.0
        Returns:
        the interpolated state
